77, \"end\": 1692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Mercury\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.373282510342567e-13, \"text\": \"Phoenix Mercury\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Mercury\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Mercury\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Clark handled thedecision with class, it has still caused people to lose their minds, as have most thingsinvolving Clark recently.\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 2041, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite struggling from the field early in her professional career, she's 14th in the WNBA in scoring at 16.8 points per game, which is right around where Taurasi and Ionescu are.\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2198, \"end\": 2205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diana_Taurasi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.4410234508499176e-69, \"text\": \"Taurasi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diana_Taurasi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diana_Taurasi\"}, {\"begin\": 2210, \"end\": 2217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabrina_Ionescu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9127420478145874e-37, \"text\": \"Ionescu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabrina_Ionescu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabrina_Ionescu\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's also fourth in assists, 18th in steals and 24th in rebounding  There was a case to be made for Clark to be on the roster, but Team USA went another direction.\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2355, \"end\": 2363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999929051884218, \"rank\": 7.055284168604088e-06, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now there are only four years to debate whether she belongs on the roster for the 2028 Los Angeles Olympics.\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2496, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In theory, Diana Taurasi's roster spot will be open by then.\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2557, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2508, \"end\": 2521, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diana_Taurasi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Diana Taurasi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diana_Taurasi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diana_Taurasi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The women's Olympic basketball tournament begins on Sunday, July 28 with Team USA playing their first Group C game against Japan on Monday, July 29 at 3pm EST.\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2718, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2632, \"end\": 2640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999929051884218, \"rank\": 7.055284168604088e-06, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2661, \"end\": 2668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_FIFA_U-17_Women's_World_Cup\", \"score\": 0.5899073326910018, \"rank\": 0.6951814008644774, \"text\": \"Group C\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_FIFA_U-17_Women's_World_Cup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_FIFA_U-17_Women's_World_Cup\"}, {\"begin\": 2682, \"end\": 2687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9365715874323162, \"rank\": 0.06769855721392146,